# 🕊️ Just Justice

<div align="center">

  <img src="assets/palestine-flag.png" alt="Palestine Flag" width="220" />

  <h3 style="color:#d9534f;">❤️</h3>

  <p><strong>
  "O you who have believed, be persistently standing firm for Allah, witnesses in justice.<br>
  And do not let the hatred of a people prevent you from being just. Be just: that is nearer to righteousness.<br>
  And fear Allah; indeed, Allah is acquainted with what you do."
  </strong></p>

  <p style="font-size:1.2rem;">
  <strong>
  يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ كُونُوا۟ قَوَّٰمِينَ لِلَّهِ شُهَدَآءَ بِٱلْقِسْطِ ۖ<br>
  وَلَا يَجْرِمَنَّكُمْ شَنَـَٔانُ قَوْمٍ عَلَ

